<h1>Meeting Planner's Guide</h1>
<strong>Meeting Guide</strong>

Find helpful connections in the business world to make your meetings run smoothly. Below you will find resources on all topics relating to business meetings. What you will need to plan before the meetings like travel arrangements and accommodations. What you will need during the meeting in regards to Audio-Visual and computer rentals. This directory will also provide resources to marketing and PowerPoint tutorials so you can have the tools to make your meeting stand out from the rest.
<blockquote>With so many moving parts involved in planning events, why not consult one easy list for everything you need?</blockquote>
<strong>Flight/Transportation</strong>

<a href="http://www.priceline.com/" rel="nofollow">Price Line</a> Find huge savings when you book your flight, hotel, rental car together with price line.

<a href="http://www.orbitz.com/" rel="nofollow">Orbitz</a> Use the Orbitz Price Assurance to find the lowest deals. Choose from Flight + Hotel, Flight + Car, Hotel + Car, or book all three.

<a href="http://www.travelocity.com/" rel="nofollow">Travelocity</a> Plan all of your transportation and accommodation needs in one place whether it be by car, rail or air.

<strong>Conference Centers </strong>

