<a href="http://www.business.com/directory/advertising_and_marketing/event_and_conference_planning/conference_and_convention_centers/" rel="nofollow">Business.com</a> Provides a directory of locations where organizations have had conferences and conventions. Easy to book your next meeting space or company event.

<strong>Catering</strong>

<a href="http://www.gatheringguide.com/event_categories/caterers_catering.html" rel="nofollow">Gathering Guide</a> Find a Catering company based on your own unique meeting requirements.

<a href="http://www.respond.com/catering-services/find.html" rel="nofollow">Respond.com</a> Search for catering services for meetings, company parties, weddings or corporate events.

<a href="http://catering-services-directory.com/" rel="nofollow">Catering Services Directory</a> Find caterers in your area and also find great articles on how to choose the best catering service, best food and a guide to serving alcohol.

